remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="2e477-178">ActiveX 数据对象（ADO）与 ADO.NET 之间的链接是一种单向操作，你可以将数据从 ADO 复制到 <xref:System.Data.DataSet>，但对数据的任何更新都必须由 ADO.NET 进行处理。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-178">The link between ActiveX Data Objects (ADO) and ADO.NET is a one-way operation in that you can copy data from ADO to the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, but any updates to the data must be handled by ADO.NET.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2e477-179">当完成 <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter.Fill%2A> 操作时，<xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter.Fill%2A> 方法的此重载不会关闭输入 `Recordset`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-179">This overload of the <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter.Fill%2A> method does not close the input `Recordset` on completion of the <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter.Fill%2A> operation.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2e477-180">当处理返回多个结果的批处理 SQL 语句时，OLE DB.NET Framework 数据提供程序的 <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter.Fill%2A> 和 <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.FillSchema%2A> 实现仅检索第一个结果的架构信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-180">When handling batch SQL statements that return multiple results, this implementation of <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter.Fill%2A> and <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.FillSchema%2A> for the OLE DB.NET Framework Data Provider retrieves schema information for only the first result.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2e477-181"><xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter.Fill%2A> 操作将行添加到 <xref:System.Data.DataSet>中的指定目标 <xref:System.Data.DataTable> 对象中，如果该对象尚不存在，则创建 <xref:System.Data.DataTable> 该对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-181">The <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter.Fill%2A> operation adds the rows to the specified destination <xref:System.Data.DataTable> object in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, creating the <xref:System.Data.DataTable> object if it does not already exist.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e477-182">创建 <xref:System.Data.DataTable> 对象时，<xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter.Fill%2A> 操作通常只创建列名称元数据。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-182">When you create a <xref:System.Data.DataTable> object, the <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter.Fill%2A> operation ordinarily creates only column name metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e477-183">但是，如果 <xref:System.Data.Common.DataAdapter.MissingSchemaAction%2A> 属性设置为 `AddWithKey`，则还会创建相应的主键和约束。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-183">However, if the <xref:System.Data.Common.DataAdapter.MissingSchemaAction%2A> property is set to `AddWithKey`, appropriate primary keys and constraints are also created.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2e477-184">您可以在同一 <xref:System.Data.DataTable>上多次使用 <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter.Fill%2A> 方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-184">You can use the <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter.Fill%2A> method multiple times on the same <xref:System.Data.DataTable>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e477-185">如果存在主键，则传入行与已存在的匹配行合并在一起。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-185">If a primary key exists, incoming rows are merged with matching rows that already exist.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e477-186">如果主键不存在，将在 <xref:System.Data.DataTable>中追加传入行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-186">If no primary key exists, incoming rows are appended to the <xref:System.Data.DataTable>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e477-187">如果主键信息存在，则会对所有重复行进行协调，并且仅在对应于 <xref:System.Data.DataSet>的 <xref:System.Data.DataTable> 中出现一次。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-187">If primary key information is present, any duplicate rows are reconciled and only appear one time in the <xref:System.Data.DataTable> that corresponds to the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e477-188">可以通过 <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.FillSchema%2A>、指定 <xref:System.Data.DataTable>的 <xref:System.Data.DataTable.PrimaryKey%2A> 属性或将 <xref:System.Data.Common.DataAdapter.MissingSchemaAction%2A> 属性设置为 `AddWithKey`来设置主键信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-188">Primary key information may be set either through <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.FillSchema%2A>, by specifying the <xref:System.Data.DataTable.PrimaryKey%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.DataTable>, or by setting the <xref:System.Data.Common.DataAdapter.MissingSchemaAction%2A> property to `AddWithKey`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2e477-189">如果 <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> 返回 OUTER JOIN 的结果，则 `DataAdapter` 不会为生成的 <xref:System.Data.DataTable.PrimaryKey%2A> 设置 <xref:System.Data.DataTable>值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-189">If the <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> returns the results of an OUTER JOIN, the `DataAdapter` does not set a <xref:System.Data.DataTable.PrimaryKey%2A> value for the resulting <xref:System.Data.DataTable>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e477-190">必须显式定义主键，以确保正确解析重复行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-190">You must explicitly define the primary key to make sure that duplicate rows are resolved correctly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e477-191">有关详细信息，请参阅[定义主键](/dotnet/framework/data/adonet/dataset-datatable-dataview/defining-primary-keys)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-191">For more information, see [Defining Primary Keys](/dotnet/framework/data/adonet/dataset-datatable-dataview/defining-primary-keys).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2e477-192">若要在 OLE DB 的 .NET Framework 数据提供程序中正常工作，`AddWithKey` 要求本机 OLE DB 提供程序通过设置 DBPROP_UNIQUEROWS 属性来获取所需的主键信息，然后通过检查 DBCOLUMN_KEYCOLUMN 中的 `IColumnsRowset`来确定哪些列是主键列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-192">To function correctly with the .NET Framework Data Provider for OLE DB, `AddWithKey` requires that the native OLE DB provider obtains required primary key information by setting the DBPROP_UNIQUEROWS property, and then determines which columns are primary key columns by examining DBCOLUMN_KEYCOLUMN in the `IColumnsRowset`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e477-193">或者，用户可以在每个 <xref:System.Data.DataTable>上显式设置 primary key 约束。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-193">Alternatively the user may explicitly set the primary key constraints on each <xref:System.Data.DataTable>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e477-194">这可以确保更新与现有记录匹配的传入记录，而不是追加。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-194">This makes sure that incoming records that match existing records are updated instead of appended.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2e477-195">如果 <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter> 在填充 <xref:System.Data.DataTable>时遇到重复的列，则它将使用模式 "*columnname*1"、"*columnname*2"、"*columnname*3" 等来为后续列生成名称。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-195">If the <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter> encounters duplicate columns while populating a <xref:System.Data.DataTable>, it generates names for the subsequent columns, using the pattern "*columnname*1", "*columnname*2", "*columnname*3", and so on.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e477-196">为空列名添加到 <xref:System.Data.DataTable>中，为第一列使用空字符串，后跟 "1"、"2"、"3" 等。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-196">Empty column names are added to the <xref:System.Data.DataTable>, using an empty string for the first column, followed by "1", "2", "3", and so on for the subsequent empty columns.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2e477-197">ADO `Recordset` 或 `Record` 对象的值将转换为 <xref:System.Data.DataSet>中存储的公共语言运行时类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-197">Values in ADO `Recordset` or `Record` objects are converted to common language runtime types for storage in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span></span>  
  
> [!CAUTION]
>  <span data-ttu-id="2e477-198">当填充操作完成时，<xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter.Fill%2A> 方法的此重载不会隐式调用 ADO 对象上的 `Close`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-198">This overload of the <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter.Fill%2A> method does not implicitly call `Close` on the ADO object when the fill operation is complete.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e477-199">因此，在使用完 ADO `Recordset` 或 `Record` 对象时，请始终调用 `Close`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-199">Therefore, always call `Close` when you are finished using ADO `Recordset` or `Record` objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e477-200">这可以确保与数据源的基础连接及时发布，并且还可防止由于在现有引用仍然存在时被垃圾回收回收的非托管 ADO 对象而导致可能的访问冲突。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-200">This makes sure that the underlying connection to a data source is released in a timely manner, and also prevents possible access violations because of unmanaged ADO objects being reclaimed by garbage collection when existing references still exist.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2e477-201">如果对 `DataAdapter` 调用 `TableMappings.Add` 方法，并将源表参数显式映射为空字符串，则将使用源表成功填充数据集，但不会填充数据集。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-201">When you call the `TableMappings.Add` method on a `DataAdapter` and you explicitly map the source table parameter to an empty string, the dataset is successfully filled using the source table, but the dataset will be populated with nothing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e477-202">例如，在下面的示例中，`rDataSet` 将填充 "无"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-202">For example, in the following example, `rDataSet` will be populated with nothing.</span></span>  
  
```  
rAdapter.TableMappings.Add("source table", "");  
rAdapter.Fill(rDataSet, "source table");     
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2e477-203">此示例演示如何在处理多个结果时跳过结果。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-203">This example shows how you can skip a result when dealing with multiple results.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2e477-204">下面的示例使用 <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter> 使用 ADO `Recordset`填充 <xref:System.Data.DataTable>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-204">The following example uses an <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter> to fill a <xref:System.Data.DataTable> using an ADO `Recordset`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e477-205">此示例假设已创建 ADO `Recordset`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e477-205">This example assumes that you have created an ADO `Recordset`.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Dim custDA As OleDbDataAdapter = New OleDbDataAdapter()  
     Dim custDS As DataSet = New DataSet  
     Dim custTable As DataTable = New DataTable("Customers")  
     custTable.Columns.Add("CustomerID", Type.GetType("System.String"))  
     custTable.Columns.Add("CompanyName", Type.GetType("System.String"))  
     custDS.Tables.Add(custTable)  
     'Use ADO objects from ADO library (msado15.dll) imported  
     ' as.NET library ADODB.dll using TlbImp.exe  
     Dim adoConn As ADODB.Connection = New ADODB.Connection()  
     Dim adoRS As ADODB.Recordset = New ADODB.Recordset()  
     adoConn.Open("Provider=SQLOLEDB;Data Source=localhost;Initial Catalog=Northwind;Integrated Security=SSPI;", "", "", -1)  
     adoRS.Open("SELECT CustomerID, CompanyName FROM Customers", adoConn, ADODB.CursorTypeEnum.adOpenForwardOnly, ADODB.LockTypeEnum.adLockReadOnly, 1)  
     custDA.Fill(custTable, adoRS)  
     adoRS.Close()  
     adoConn.Close()  
```  
  
```csharp  
OleDbDataAdapter custDA = new OleDbDataAdapter();  
     DataSet custDS = new DataSet();  
     DataTable custTable = new DataTable("Customers");  
     custTable.Columns.Add("CustomerID", typeof(String));  
     custTable.Columns.Add("CompanyName", typeof(String));  
     custDS.Tables.Add(custTable);  
     //Use ADO objects from ADO library (msado15.dll) imported  
     //  as.NET library ADODB.dll using TlbImp.exe  
     ADODB.Connection adoConn = new ADODB.Connection();  
     ADODB.Recordset adoRS = new ADODB.Recordset();  
     adoConn.Open("Provider=SQLOLEDB;Data Source=localhost;Initial Catalog=Northwind;Integrated Security=SSPI;", "", "", -1);  
     adoRS.Open("SELECT CustomerID, CompanyName FROM Customers", adoConn, ADODB.CursorTypeEnum.adOpenForwardOnly, ADODB.LockTypeEnum.adLockReadOnly, 1);  
     custDA.Fill(custTable, adoRS);  
     adoRS.Close();  
     adoConn.Close();  
```
